meaning you bring to the work.

00:44:45.620 --> 00:44:48.290
And there are people
here, I'm sure,

00:44:48.290 --> 00:44:50.860
who are not enjoying
meaningful work,

00:44:50.860 --> 00:44:52.600
but who look like they are.

00:44:52.600 --> 00:44:54.270
And the opposite is also true.

00:44:54.270 --> 00:44:56.600
There may be people who
are on the security force

00:44:56.600 --> 00:44:58.910
or helping with valet
parking or doing things

00:44:58.910 --> 00:45:01.250
that you think aren't
all that meaningful.

00:45:01.250 --> 00:45:04.700
But they may bring
meaning to those jobs

00:45:04.700 --> 00:45:08.250
in a way that is
very, very authentic.

00:45:08.250 --> 00:45:11.490
I like to say that the people
who find meaningful work

00:45:11.490 --> 00:45:15.220
are a legion of the
secretly successful.

00:45:15.220 --> 00:45:17.340
They are not people
that you read about.

00:45:17.340 --> 00:45:20.440
They're not people that
you get stories about.

00:45:20.440 --> 00:45:23.190
They're people who've found
success for themselves

00:45:23.190 --> 00:45:28.030
in the meaning of what they do,
in the relationships they have,

00:45:28.030 --> 00:45:30.790
in their ability to
love and be loved.

00:45:30.790 --> 00:45:37.760
And it's not so clear that the
obvious things that we value

00:45:37.760 --> 00:45:38.790
